To start the project, Run the (index.html) file by this command in terminal: 'node server.js'
Access the page on http://localhost:9000

Make sure the Apache and MySql modules are active in XAMPP server.
Make sure that the databases and tables are available (Queries are available in a file : Queries).

You have to install the following packages:
1. express  (npm install express)
2. mysql
3. body-parser
4. path  //optional



Technologies used:
1. HTML
2. CSS
3. JavaScript
4. Ajax
5. Bootstrap
6. Typed.JS
7. Node.JS
8. Express.JS
9. mysql